divs: Sighting Detailson saturday june 23, aprox. 11:30 am three sets of two usa fighter jets flew over our camp ground area and seemed to be flying very low. Didn't think that was normal? Within 15 min later I was near the open water setting up my beach chair and this object caught my eye. I then grabbed my camera and two pictures. I have had the film developed and have proof of this event. The loction of event was on the Hudson river, nine miles north of lake lucerne. If you orgazation is enterested in my photos, feel free to call me at home. 518-731-7580
